043   /** Default serializer, all default settings.*/

046   /**
047    * Creates a new builder for this object.
048    *
049    * @return A new builder.
050    */

053   }

749
750      // </FluentSetters>
751   }
752
753   //-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
754   // Instance
755   //-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
756
757   private final Map<ClassMeta<?>,CsvClassMeta> csvClassMetas = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
758   private final Map<BeanPropertyMeta,CsvBeanPropertyMeta> csvBeanPropertyMetas = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
759
760   /**
761    * Constructor.
762    *
763    * @param builder The builder for this object.
764    */
765   public CsvSerializer(Builder builder) {
766      super(builder);
767   }
768
769   @Override /* Context */
770   public Builder copy() {
771      return new Builder(this);
772   }
773
774   @Override /* Context */
775   public CsvSerializerSession.Builder createSession() {
776      return CsvSerializerSession.create(this);
777   }
778
779   @Override /* Context */
780   public CsvSerializerSession getSession() {
781      return createSession().build();
782   }
783
784   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
785   // Extended metadata
786   //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
787
788   @Override /* CsvMetaProvider */
789   public CsvClassMeta getCsvClassMeta(ClassMeta<?> cm) {
790      CsvClassMeta m = csvClassMetas.get(cm);
791      if (m == null) {
792         m = new CsvClassMeta(cm, this);
793         csvClassMetas.put(cm, m);
794      }
795      return m;
796   }
797
798   @Override /* CsvMetaProvider */
799   public CsvBeanPropertyMeta getCsvBeanPropertyMeta(BeanPropertyMeta bpm) {
800      if (bpm == null)
801         return CsvBeanPropertyMeta.DEFAULT;
802      CsvBeanPropertyMeta m = csvBeanPropertyMetas.get(bpm);
803      if (m == null) {
804         m = new CsvBeanPropertyMeta(bpm.getDelegateFor(), this);
805         csvBeanPropertyMetas.put(bpm, m);
806      }
807      return m;
808   }
